title: Senator Faisal pays tribute to PAF Ghazis, Martyrs
content:
ISLAMABAD, Sep 07 (APP): Chairman Senate Standing Committee on Information and Broadcasting Senator Faisal Javed Khan on Tuesday paid a glowing tribute to Pakistan Air Force (PAF) Ghazis, Martyrs and their families.
On #PakAirForceDay todayAll our gratitude to our 'warriors in the air'. Tribute to our Ghazis, Martyrs & their families who have given countless sacrifices for safeguarding our nation#MeinUra @AliZafarsays#PakistanAirforce  #PakistanZindabad  https://t.co/I8fS3AmXMz
— Faisal Javed Khan (@FaisalJavedKhan) September 7, 2021
In a tweet, he said, on Pakistan Air Force Day today, all our gratitude goes to our ‘warriors in the air, Ghazis, martyrs and their families who have given countless sacrifices for safeguarding our nation,” he said.
